Claude Code's entry point. Import the shared conventions, then add only Claude-specific notes.

## Project conventions

@AGENTS.md

## Claude Code specifics

- Delegate to the sub-agents in `.claude/agents/` for their specialty (planner, code-reviewer,
  debugger, test-writer, security-reviewer, docs-writer).
- Use the slash commands in `.claude/commands/` for standard workflows.
- Hooks (`.claude/settings.json`) enforce formatting and protect sensitive paths.

## Before saying "done"

Run the project's tests and formatter (see AGENTS.md) and read the output before reporting success.
